name: Listened to Ohio State beats Notre Dame, Oregon demolishes Colorado + coaches sounding off in Week 4

content.html:
Stew and Bruce discuss Ohio State’s win over Notre Dame in a game where both teams impressed, Oregon’s beatdown of Colorado, and USC defeating ASU. Also, thoughts on FSU-Clemson, Penn State shutting down Iowa, a week of angry coaches, and it’s all wrapped up with shout outs.
